### ==========================================
### report-app.http
### Lưu ý: Gateway hiện chưa có controller cho Reports.
### Tạm thời dùng health endpoints để kiểm tra kết nối services.
### Khi bổ sung routes cho báo cáo, có thể dùng các mẫu bên dưới.
### ==========================================

# Base variables (fallback nếu chưa chọn environment trong http-client.env.json)
@hostname = localhost
@port = 3000
@gateway = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### 1) HEALTH - Tổng quan NATS connection
GET {{gateway}}/health

###

### 2) HEALTH - Services status & latency
GET {{gateway}}/health/services

###

### (MẪU - CHƯA ACTIVE) Reports qua Gateway - đề xuất:
### GET {{gateway}}/reports/sales-summary?fromAt=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&toAt=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
### GET {{gateway}}/reports/product-performance?fromAt=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&toAt=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
### GET {{gateway}}/reports/user-cohort?fromAt=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&toAt=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z

